2001-3400 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE of Louisiana v. Patrick D. HENRY. No. 2001-K-3400. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re State of Louisiana; — Plaintiff; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Re*1169view, Parish of Orleans, Criminal District Court Div. J, No. 418-060; to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Circuit, No. 2001-KA-0333.
